Class ServerFacade

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.facade.ServerFacade
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IServerFacade

    public class ServerFacade
extends java.lang.Object
implements IServerFacade
    The ServerFacade class controls all interactions between the command classes, the handlers, and the database.
    Version:
    1.0 Build Mar, 2016.
    Author:
    Christian Riboldi, Clayton Condie, Jacob Brewer, Joshua Powers, Joshua Van Steeter
